title: Barack Obama stops in Seattle after visiting Roseburg
text: President Obama is expected to touch down at Boeing Field at 3:45 p.m. Friday, then head to the Westin Hotel in downtown Seattle for two events: a roundtable benefiting the Democratic National Committee, and a fundraiser for U.S. Sen. Patty Murray’s 2016 reelection campaign. Drivers and transit users should expect extra traffic congestion and delays. Downtown […]> ...
